title: 123 Ways to Look at Life
description:
123 Ways to Look at Life by Bernardo Moya

Overview: "This book will help you to assess what is important in your life. In these times of uncertainty, stress and difficulty, we need to focus on the little things that help make us who we are and think. Whatever the problems we face in our lives, it's these little things that are the most important in finding and maintaining happiness." - Bernardo Moya. In his first book, 123 Ways To See Life, Bernardo Moya explores a variety of different emotional perspectives that will guide you towards the best version of yourself. 123 inspiring quotes and thoughts will help you to rediscover and reinvent yourself, starting at the very roots of your weaknesses or concerns. This book will inspire you, make you think and help you to grow
